###
### UPDATE SENSOR METADATA
### Note: Can only update name, location, and status
### Attempting to update value or unit will return 400 error
###

### Update sensor metadata (name, location, status only)
PUT http://localhost:3001/api/sensors/YOUR_SENSOR_ID_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Temperature Sensor - Main Floor",
  "location": "Kitchen",
  "status": "active"
}

### Try to update value (will fail with 400 error)
PUT http://localhost:3001/api/sensors/YOUR_SENSOR_ID_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "value": 99.9,
  "status": "active"
}

### Set sensor to maintenance mode
PUT http://localhost:3001/api/sensors/YOUR_SENSOR_ID_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "maintenance"
}

### Delete sensor
DELETE http://localhost:3001/api/sensors/YOUR_SENSOR_ID_HERE
